history.content:
Hi Folks

I will be holding office hours relating to the Bloom Filter project This Wednesday and Thursday (tentative, might reschedule Thursday to be later in week, will know for certain Wednesday).  These office hours will each be 2 hours long, and will be held in a similar format to what you are used to.

I will only be discussing the project, but I will be glad to help folks with python-related questions (although honestly the python requirements for this program are basic), and I will also clarify the requirements of the different sections.

Also, as a reminder, please post any questions regarding the Bloom filter project to piazza using the "project" tag.
